title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 105: Featuring Brent Seabrook
description:
On this week's episode, the guys are joined by three time Stanley Cup champion, Brent Seabrook, defenseman for the Chicago Blackhawks. The guys talk about the crazy ride and the three cups with Chicago, some funny Joel Quennville stories, and much more. The guys also talk Tyler Seguin and his contract situation in Dallas. Could the star center be on the move again? The guys discuss.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
